    "description": "《基地一号》是一款带有RPG元素的太空基地题材建造游戏。大型虫洞将月球撕裂并造成前所未有的自然灾害之后，[地球全球联盟]制定了“求索”太空探索计划，探索虫洞，寻找新的家园。作为“求索”计划的指挥官，你将全权掌控船队的发展，寻找珍贵矿物和适合居住的新行星—甚至可以拯救地球免受生态毁灭。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>指挥 &quot;地盟&quot; 太空站船队，穿越星系的每个角落。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471040/extras/635b84dc937a86517abcfa3549a8c979.poster.avif?t=1678321038\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471040/extras/635b84dc937a86517abcfa3549a8c979.webm?t=1678321038\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471040/extras/635b84dc937a86517abcfa3549a8c979.mp4?t=1678321038\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>在性格各异和特质多样的船员中选择自己的机组成员，以最佳的方式解决太空站上的问题。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471040/extras/d07deee9d80bb639f6b24792e7cf20ca.poster.avif?t=1678321038\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471040/extras/d07deee9d80bb639f6b24792e7cf20ca.webm?t=1678321038\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471040/extras/d07deee9d80bb639f6b24792e7cf20ca.mp4?t=1678321038\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>监控太空站网络的共享资源——电力、供暖、氧气和供水。将有限的补给在各个太空站之间合理分配是生存下去的关键！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471040/extras/2d6eec2b61d5fb85527cda72b37703f3.poster.avif?t=1678321038\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471040/extras/2d6eec2b61d5fb85527cda72b37703f3.webm?t=1678321038\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471040/extras/2d6eec2b61d5fb85527cda72b37703f3.mp4?t=1678321038\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>升级舰炮，快速解决拦路的小行星。 &quot;地盟&quot; 可以提供最好的军事专业知识来阻止太空海盗！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471040/extras/c3cf9a871f660c6896fd2017b474b038.poster.avif?t=1678321038\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471040/extras/c3cf9a871f660c6896fd2017b474b038.webm?t=1678321038\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471040/extras/c3cf9a871f660c6896fd2017b474b038.mp4?t=1678321038\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><br>打造属于你自己的“求索”远征队，听听船员带来的各种故事，探索各种未知星系。经验丰富玩家更可以根据自身的习惯和任务来建立属于自己的自定义游戏。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >“求索”就在您的掌控之中，船长！</h2><br>免责声明：目前不支持带有 M1 处理器的 Mac 系统。",
